"""
        Test that the equality operator returns False when comparing two
        AttestationCredential structs with different attestation assertions.
        """
a = objects.AttestationCredential(attestation_assertion=
    b'\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff')
b = objects.AttestationCredential(attestation_assertion=
    b'\x11\x11\x11\x11\x11\x11\x11\x11')
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
